  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba3 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1!",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Complaint to the Jaffna Police against those who lost the package!",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A complaint has been registered at the Jaffna Police Station regarding a private bus engaged in the Jaffna-Colombo transport service who misplaced a package sent through the package services and spoke inappropriate words to the person who was to receive the package in Jaffna.",
        "A young man from Jaffna purchased a spare part worth 6 thousand rupees for his motorcycle by contacting people in Colombo, and it was sent to Jaffna through the package services of a private bus operating between Jaffna and Colombo at a fee of 600 rupees.",
        "When they went to get the said package in Jaffna, they irresponsibly replied that the package was lost and when asked to give the price of the item in the package due to the package being lost, they spoke inappropriate words and behaved in a rude manner.",
        "At the same time, we are very saddened by the fact that they used their package services and sent the packages recklessly, left them wrong, and spoke inappropriate words without any responsibility. He expressed concern that due to the economic crisis in the country, we are being crushed in every way."
      ],
